OL,3,CRadio 2 DJ Scott Mills sacked by BBC
OL,4,Cover 'personal conduct'
OL,6,FRadio presenter Scott Mills has
OL,7,Freportedly been sacked from his BBC
OL,8,Fjob over allegations relating to his
OL,9,F"personal conduct".
OL,11,FIn a statement, the BBC said: "While
OL,12,Fwe do not comment on matters relating
OL,13,Fto individuals, we can confirm Scott
OL,14,FMills is no longer contracted to work
OL,15,Fwith the BBC."
OL,17,FOn Tuesday March 24, Mills ended his
OL,18,FBBC Radio 2 breakfast show saying he
OL,19,Fwould be "back tomorrow".
OL,26,@sD@_OUwD@NO]
