OL,3,CRadio 2 DJ Scott Mills sacked by BBC
OL,4,Cover 'personal conduct'
OL,6,FBut it was BBC broadcaster Gary Davies
OL,7,Fwho hosted the show the following
OL,8,Fmorning, saying he was "in for Scott
OL,9,FMills".
OL,11,FThe 53-year-old had been working on
OL,12,Fthe breakfast show since taking over
OL,13,Ffrom Zoe Ball in January 2025.
OL,15,FPrior this, the DJ has hosted various
OL,16,Fother shows on Radio 1, 2 and 5.
OL,18,FThis is a breaking news story, more to
OL,19,Ffollow.
